Package org.tedros.fx.annotation.presenter

Annotation Type TSelectionModalPresenter

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(TYPE)
public @interface TSelectionModalPresenter
     The selection modal view settings
    Author:
    Davis Gordon

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element Description
      boolean allowsMultipleSelections
      If true allows the user to select more than one item, but this must be set according the field type which will received the selected items.
      TPaginator paginator
      The paginator settings, the following property is required: entityClass - the entity of type ITEntity to search modelViewClass - the model view class with the fields of the entityClass which was configured for the tableView this fields is the columns values.
      TTableView tableView
      The table view build settings to show the search result.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
      double listViewMaxWidth
      The list view max width
      double listViewMinWidth
      The list view min width
      TPresenter presenter
      The modal view build settings

    • Element Detail

      • allowsMultipleSelections

        boolean allowsMultipleSelections
        If true allows the user to select more than one item, but this must be set according the field type which will received the selected items. If the field type is a SimpleObjectProperty than this must be false because the field can hold just one value but if the field type is an ITObservableList this can be true.

      • tableView

        TTableView tableView
        The table view build settings to show the search result.

      • paginator

        TPaginator paginator
          The paginator settings, the following property is required:
  
  entityClass - the entity of type ITEntity to search
  
  modelViewClass - the model view class with the fields of the entityClass
  which was configured for the tableView this fields is the columns values.
  
  serviceName - the jndi name for the ejb service

      • listViewMaxWidth

        double listViewMaxWidth
        The list view max width
        Default:
        250.0

      • listViewMinWidth

        double listViewMinWidth
        The list view min width
        Default:
        250.0

      • presenter

        TPresenter presenter
        The modal view build settings
        Default:
        @org.tedros.fx.annotation.presenter.TPresenter(behavior=@org.tedros.fx.annotation.presenter.TBehavior(type=org.tedros.fx.presenter.modal.behavior.TSelectionModalBehavior.class), decorator=@org.tedros.fx.annotation.presenter.TDecorator(type=org.tedros.fx.presenter.modal.decorator.TSelectionModalDecorator.class, viewTitle="#{tedros.fxapi.view.modal.selection.title}"), type=org.tedros.fx.presenter.dynamic.TDynaPresenter.class)
